		<item>
		<title>Building a 20-Touchpoint Revenue Orchestration System That Eliminates the &#8220;Random Acts of Marketing&#8221; Chaos and Delivers $19.40 Pipeline Per $1 Invested</title>
		<link>https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/case_studies/building-a-20-touchpoint-revenue-orchestration-system-that-eliminates-the-random-acts-of-marketing-chaos-and-delivers-19-40-pipeline-per-1-invested/</link>
					<comments>https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/case_studies/building-a-20-touchpoint-revenue-orchestration-system-that-eliminates-the-random-acts-of-marketing-chaos-and-delivers-19-40-pipeline-per-1-invested/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 10 Dec 2025 12:45:14 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Banking]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[FinTech]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[SDR Cost]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/?post_type=case_studies&#038;p=938</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>A mid-market financial advisory firm had successfully executed (Content Foundation) (LinkedIn Distribution), generating consistent organic traffic and social engagement. However, their revenue conversion was suffering from the same disease plaguing 78% of B2B companies: fragmented funnel syndrome.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/case_studies/building-a-20-touchpoint-revenue-orchestration-system-that-eliminates-the-random-acts-of-marketing-chaos-and-delivers-19-40-pipeline-per-1-invested/">Building a 20-Touchpoint Revenue Orchestration System That Eliminates the &#8220;Random Acts of Marketing&#8221; Chaos and Delivers $19.40 Pipeline Per $1 Invested</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency">Our Work</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>A mid-market financial advisory firm had successfully executed (Content Foundation) (LinkedIn Distribution), generating consistent organic traffic and social engagement. However, their revenue conversion was suffering from the same disease plaguing 78% of B2B companies: fragmented funnel syndrome.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/case_studies/building-a-20-touchpoint-revenue-orchestration-system-that-eliminates-the-random-acts-of-marketing-chaos-and-delivers-19-40-pipeline-per-1-invested/">Building a 20-Touchpoint Revenue Orchestration System That Eliminates the &#8220;Random Acts of Marketing&#8221; Chaos and Delivers $19.40 Pipeline Per $1 Invested</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency">Our Work</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
					<wfw:commentRss>https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/case_studies/building-a-20-touchpoint-revenue-orchestration-system-that-eliminates-the-random-acts-of-marketing-chaos-and-delivers-19-40-pipeline-per-1-invested/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
			<slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
		
		
			</item>
		<item>
		<title>Transforming Sporadic LinkedIn Posts into a Systematic Pipeline Engine for FinTech Sales Teams</title>
		<link>https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/case_studies/transforming-sporadic-linkedin-posts-into-a-systematic-pipeline-engine-for-fintech-sales-teams/</link>
					<comments>https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/case_studies/transforming-sporadic-linkedin-posts-into-a-systematic-pipeline-engine-for-fintech-sales-teams/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 10 Dec 2025 06:50:16 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Banking]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[FinTech]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[SDR Cost]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/?post_type=case_studies&#038;p=882</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>The FinTech client&#8217;s sales and leadership team (12 executives, 8 senior bankers, 5 portfolio managers) were posting inconsistently on LinkedIn—averaging 6 posts/month total across 25 profiles. Posts had no strategic objectives, content themes were random, and there was zero conversion mechanism beyond &#8220;hope someone comments.&#8221;</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/case_studies/transforming-sporadic-linkedin-posts-into-a-systematic-pipeline-engine-for-fintech-sales-teams/">Transforming Sporadic LinkedIn Posts into a Systematic Pipeline Engine for FinTech Sales Teams</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency">Our Work</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p></p>



<p>The FinTech client&#8217;s sales and leadership team (12 executives, 8 senior bankers, 5 portfolio managers) were posting inconsistently on LinkedIn—averaging 6 posts/month total across 25 profiles. Posts had no strategic objectives, content themes were random, and there was zero conversion mechanism beyond &#8220;hope someone comments.&#8221;<br><br><br></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/case_studies/transforming-sporadic-linkedin-posts-into-a-systematic-pipeline-engine-for-fintech-sales-teams/">Transforming Sporadic LinkedIn Posts into a Systematic Pipeline Engine for FinTech Sales Teams</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency">Our Work</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
					<wfw:commentRss>https://ourwork.electricoctopus.agency/case_studies/transforming-sporadic-linkedin-posts-into-a-systematic-pipeline-engine-for-fintech-sales-teams/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
			<slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
		
		
			</item>
